<div class="row">
  <div class="col-xl-8 offset-xl-2">
    <h1>Creating an Account and Registering People</h1>
    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap">
      <div class="card card-body m-2 text-white bg-info">
        1. Register as Account Owner
      </div>
      <div class="card card-body m-2 text-center text-white bg-dark">
        <%= fa_icon("arrow-right") %>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-body m-2 text-white bg-info" >
        2. Create School Account
      </div>
      <div class="card card-body m-2 text-center text-white bg-dark">
        <%= fa_icon("arrow-right") %>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-body m-2 text-white bg-info" style="max-width: 25rem;">
        3. Invite people to register as school members via email using the form
        in this application.
      </div>
      <div class="card card-body m-2 text-center text-white bg-dark">
        <%= fa_icon("arrow-right") %>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-body m-2 text-white bg-info" style="max-width: 18rem;">
        4. Person accepts invitation by clicking on the link in email.
      </div>
      <div class="card card-body m-2 text-center text-white bg-dark">
        <%= fa_icon("arrow-right") %>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-body m-2 text-white bg-info" style="max-width: 18rem;">
        5. Invited person registers with name and password.
      </div>
      <div class="card card-body m-2 text-center text-white bg-dark">
        <%= fa_icon("arrow-right") %>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-body m-2 text-white bg-info" style="max-width: 25rem;">
        6. Account owner assigns different roles to teachers, learners, parents and
        school administrators etc. respectively.
      </div>
      <div class="card card-body m-2 text-center text-white bg-dark">
        <%= fa_icon("arrow-right") %>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-body m-2 text-white bg-info" style="max-width: 18rem;">
        7. School administrators proceed to build classes and teams etc.
      </div>
      <div class="card card-body m-2 text-center text-white bg-dark">
        <%= fa_icon("arrow-right") %>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-body m-2">
        <%= link_to new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-primary' do %>
          <%= fa_icon "magic", text: "Creat a New Account" %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-xl-8 offset-xl-2 py-3">

  </div>
</div>
